ura Salaam]] (2001) * [[Lawrence Schimel]] (1991) * [[Carol Severance]] (1984) * [[Nisi Shawl]] (1992)<ref name=about>{{Cite web|url=http://www.clarionwest.org/about/|title=About us|publisher=Clarion West Writers Workshop|accessdate=March 24, 2015}}</ref> * [[Jeff Spock]] (2004) * [[Rachel Swirsky]] (2005)<ref name=2k5/> * [[Gabriel Teodros]] (2016) * [[Sheree Thomas]] (1999) * [[Amy Thomson]] (1984) * [[Gordon Van Gelder]] (1987) * [[David J. Williams]] (2007) * [[Eric M. Witchey]] (1998) * [[N. Lee Wood]] (1985)
